title: Alnutrisa Delicatesen Light
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. One of many sandwich places in North Quito, the difference is that it offers veggie-meat for the sandwiches and has an entire page of the menu devoted to vegetarian choices. Modern, nice deli feel; also sells some packaged snack foods. Located directly across from Parque La Carolina and just south of El Comercio.
